<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Number of palettes in the GBC]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12297&amp;p=139869#p139869"><![CDATA[
The GBC gets 8 palettes for sprites, and 8 palettes for backgrounds, and can freely change palette colors at any time during rendering.  Also, the background color for background palettes is not shared, so each background tile gets a full 4 colors.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Sun Jan 25, 2015 10:04 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
